  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By and large, most of it was the clothes I brought and, and the books I, I couldn't part from.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I do [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] want to mention this, this much, that my brother told me, many years later, after we knew already my parents' fate, that when my father had seen me off at the dock, or where the boat was leaving from, he turned to my brother and he said, who knows whether I will ever see him again.",
      "word_count": 67
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It so happens that my brother worked for that steamship company, which was the Hamburg America Line.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and the name of the ship was which means Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, none I knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I found very congenial company, including a, an American student who had been studying in Heidelberg and with whom I had a correspondence following my arrival here.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I considered it something of an adventure.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, once the farewells were over with, I could concentrate on just-- I, I had never done anything like this, obviously, and I, I had traveled very little [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] within Germany.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so this was a great adventure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And here, I was also going to this country that I had read about and seen so many films about.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and, and that served to distract me in those days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, this American student.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I made some other casual acquaintances, nothing lasting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I went directly to Buffalo, New York.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's where my sister lived at that time, although she didn't live there for, for very much longer after that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She moved to New York City.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
